intent.user_query: How many new customers registered each month in 2023? Show the month and the number of new customers.

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT EXTRACT(MONTH FROM RegistrationDate) AS RegistrationMonth, COUNT(*) AS NewCustomers FROM fitness_db.Customers WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM RegistrationDate) = 2023 GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY 1;

arguments.sql: SELECT EXTRACT(MONTH FROM RegistrationDate) AS RegistrationMonth, COUNT(*) AS NewCustomers FROM fitness_db.Customers WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM RegistrationDate) = 2023 GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY 1;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
